p: With the help of the Geneious Prime software suite (v. 2019.2.3; Biomatters Ltd., Auckland, New Zealand), phylogenetic analyses were performed (for details see legend Fig.Â 1). The genomes originating from the reported German case form a new and distinct cluster within the S-INDEL strains (see Fig. 1). Close relatives are three virus strains reported in 2019, two from Hungary [ 16] (accessions MH593900 and KX289955) and one from France (accession MN056942).
